Ira David Landis (12 January 1899 - 27 February, 1977) was a Mennonite minister, historian and writer. He was also a farmer in Lititz, PA.
He was editor of, and prolific contributor to, the quarterly Mennonite Research Journal, that was published from April 1960 through October 1977. He was president of the Pennsylvania German Society in 1972. Besides his own works, he also published three editions of the Martyr's Mirror in English.
